Comment: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.15,0:01:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不太正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说大家都因为疑神疑鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他人逃出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出血已经止住了  没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们待在这里不要离开  听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学  你还记得她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…不是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么果然…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同学怀疑是见崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我怀疑你才是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年是从5月开始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那5月份增加的人才是死者  难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年是从4月开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种胡言乱语谁会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见同学…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点被敕使河原杀掉时明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然自己会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不转学过来  由加利就不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不去接近不存在的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者就回归死…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同学怎么可能是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见同学  你杀了两个同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着也没用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来让你解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去由加利那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再做自相残杀这种傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽说些漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕死亡而临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为旁观者的你没有资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还能救眼前这些死得不明不白的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁观者的你什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能推动事态的只有身处险境的当事人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学也到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  风见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的话就回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀了她的话  大家都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同学也会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎不是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果杀了她还不能停止灾难的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就认了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来…就能停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我是想保护你  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你们一起杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是夜见北的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我刚从东京过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为重要的人过世了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年半前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被空罐砸到了  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是说谎也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我说你还记得呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤泽同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  要打通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过暂时走不开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过来  这就来  你就在那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学还是别来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎…难道…你要将谁给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或许会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能救她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色  因为能看见死亡的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚刚知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就知道了  但没说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我不亲手阻止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是「另一个人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这个人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三神老师  怜子阿姨是「另一个人」吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来夜见北心得之四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公私要分明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校园里不能叫我怜子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里我也算是副班主任的三神老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校其他班级有副班主任？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  学校里有副班主任的只有三年三班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年教室的书桌是够用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而灾难4月就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺一个书桌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎  她在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同学  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死者回归死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  怜子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吗  这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没弄错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一弄错人的话  我就把怜子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见崎说过的也好  眼睛的事也好  都是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了  我看到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年半前  我看到了三神老师被杀的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起…打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么  小怜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一年半前  是在宠物店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样  一年半后的夜见山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年半前  你被空罐砸到了  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人死后都要办葬礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼真是…太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可怜了  理津子  怜子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怜子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怜子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸已经不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以  不过体育课还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不记得三神老师的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点担心  榊原同学会不会成为第9个牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了8个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说  8月的死者一共10名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两个是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高林同学的外公外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高林同学死了之后  他们的精神状态一直不太稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三神老师是在一年半前的秋天去世的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜见山河被杀人魔刺杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是记不太清楚了  今年的死者是三神老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话前年因为灾难死亡的有7人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  红叉记号有7处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前年的档案里有写着赤泽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是赤泽同学的表哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车送你们一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我们没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  回家路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…  灾难已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候知道怜子阿姨  三神老师是「另一个人」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你了也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没办法对榊原同学开口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三神老师  叫怜子阿姨的  是你重要的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一趟那边的游乐园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:21:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不坐那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我从医院给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到手机上却怎么也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个之后被我扔河里了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人讨厌的机器  没必要一直和外界联系着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  马上就会给我买新的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买好新手机后  可以偶尔给你打个电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.34,0:22:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔的话可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这个从望月同学那儿拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怜子阿姨  拍在照片上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎谁都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连望月也没看见怜子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:23:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色呢  怜子阿姨的颜色是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见死的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后的未来  我们会渐渐遗忘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月开始的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕着三神怜子发生的各种事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么不想忘记？想一直记着？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是停止灾难的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.56,0:25:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么理解是你们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一定要三思后再去着手实行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.00,0:25:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细考虑清楚  和周围的朋友们商量好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.12,0:25:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让自己后悔


